race.comment: GOODTIME IN TEXAS (7) started at $7.30 last time and ran below expectations, finishing sixth and beaten 1.5 lengths at this track (Dirt) over 229m. Faces an easier assignment so she is set to turn things around. REAL BAD CATTY (5) got home by a nose last time out over 229m at this track (Dirt). Has a good record at this track with two wins and three minor placings. Backmarker who gets home hard. Will prove tough to beat. AKILES (6) returns from a layoff of ten weeks. Worth noting he filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last prep over 302m at Sam Houston Park. Has to be respected. MAJESTIC COCKTAIL (11) was beaten 1.75 lengths into ninth over 274m at Delta Downs seven weeks ago. No surprise to see him in the mix.
